  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the grill to medium-high heat.",
    "Cut the bacon into 1-inch pieces and set aside.",
    "In a small bowl, whisk together the gochujang, soy sauce, brown sugar, rice vinegar, and ground black pepper.",
    "Add the gochujang mixture, green chilies, green onions, Korean chili flakes, sesame oil, sesame seeds, and Korean chili paste to the bowl with the bacon and toss to coat.",
    "Grill the bacon mixture for 2-3 minutes per side, or until the bacon is charred and caramelized.",
    "Transfer the bacon mixture to a serving dish and serve immediately.",
    "Garnish with additional green onions and serve with steamed rice or noodles, if desired."
  ],
